First Announcement

CT2011 will be held in Vancouver, Canada, from July 17 to July 23, 2011. It
will begin with a reception at Gage Towers on the University of British
Columbia campus at 6pm on Sunday July 17 and will end at 1pm on Saturday July
23.

Programme Committee
  	Michael Barr
  	George Janelidze
         Steve Lack
  	Tom Leinster
  	Susan Niefield
  	Diana Rodelo
  	Pino Rosolini
  	Myles Tierney
  	Richard Wood (Chairman)

Organizing Committee
  	John MacDonald
  	Jorge Picado
  	Richard Wood

The conference website is http://www.mat.uc.pt/~ct2011

Thanks to Jorge for constructing the website and to Richard both for agreeing
to be Programme Chairman and for selecting the other members of the Programme
Committee.

Further announcements will be made to this list regarding abstract submission,
housing, conference fees and other details as they become available.
Alternatively, you may just check the website from time to time.

Please pass on this information to any interested colleagues who are not on
this list.

I look forward to welcoming many of you to Vancouver next July.

John MacDonald







[For admin and other information see: http://www.mta.ca/~cat-dist/ ]

